{"tid":500372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［笑鬼死你］Ｄ１００＋泛民：我們立法會要取過半數議席，成為大多數！","createTime":"2017-12-15T16:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T18:03:23.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e76cbabb90980e00ac78f7498418c87e669aeda4","tid":500372,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2GTW3SrZ2SM?t=394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2GTW3SrZ2SM%3Ft%3D394&d=OC%2BRaEXVmetbwMqEMhrBI0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f80dab23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2GTW3SrZ2SM?t=394</a><br />\n<br />\n港大法律系副教授戴耀廷預告，未來打壓會陸續有來，但不用灰心。而拉布的確變難，但非不會發生，「議員可以發言講足15分鐘，把握機會問問題。消滅拉布係無可能！」他指，大家只要保持團結，是不會被消滅，呼籲泛民各組織要建立更緊密、更強大的政治聯盟，去抵抗威權。<br />\n戴耀廷估計，2019年將有300至400個泛民人士參選區議會，而每個要有10個義工幫助。他鼓勵泛民支持者踴躍參與和協助，讓泛民屆時拿下3、4百個議席，並爭取2020年立法會拿回過半議席。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉批評，建制派現時乘人之危修改議事規則，未來民主派一定要建制派付上更大代價，「我地要佢地輸得更慘！」呼籲只要港人未來善用手中一票，令民主派可以攻佔議會大多數，下次在立法會取得35席，未來將可在立法會收回失地。<br />\n<br />\n有功能組別嘅情況底下，請問泛民點樣拎到過半數議席？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n議會總共有70席，功能組別已經佔咗35席．．．．．．<br />\n<br />\n講大話講到連自己都呃埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1804f6e3adfc63f4de13d97e2d96801b135c1612","tid":500372,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db93f3e49341792405f0e745c53a77d0880bb5d8","tid":500372,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大奸台開咪既有邊位家眷唔係外國護照先？？？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb90ab400005c5cc219e252b21b1dae9a15f574e","tid":500372,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59d93d4064c92bba441a5449aa2e46ce87542869","tid":500372,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"泛民衰個祈福黨<br />\n<br />\n成班錫安教咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8d4afd44810de92a9c8c7ce39389f0c1a21e73","tid":500372,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁功能組別都有泛民，不過只係小數</blockquote><br />\n比例代表制嘅情況下直選議席一定起碼有十幾個畀咗建制<br />\n功能組別點拎到十幾席試問？"},{"pid":"25f3f395e52a85bb31dd80ca3480aabb17ac8b17","tid":500372,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bc244aec35e8ec06e6fae225cfd543eb4712e75","tid":500372,"uid":92072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:49:42.000Z","msg":"民主黨快啲走入中聯辦傾傾啦"},{"pid":"082894de3cf8e5fe31b1f490262f2a0f0c9d6b65","tid":500372,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"十足十亞視咁"}]}